-- Qantas CEO Joyce Says Carrier Plans to Revamp Its In-Flight Food, Lounges
-- Robert Fenner
-- 2010-07-27T23:06:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/qantas-ceo-joyce-says-carrier-plans-to-revamp-its-in-flight-food-lounges.html

          
          
             Qantas Airways Ltd. will revamp its
in-flight food and will have new in-flight entertainment,
according to notes from Chief Executive Officer Alan Joyce on a
speech to be delivered in Sydney today.  
